snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reacts To Amber Heard Being In Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Reacts To Amber Heard Being In Aquaman 2

Celebrity break-ups are a tricky thing. While ending relationships is difficult for all of us, this is exasperated when splitting becomes a public affair. Actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard know this all too well, as the former couple has been battling in the press, as well as in court. And now there are rumors about Heard still being a star in Aquaman 2.

Johnny Depp fans have already famously petitioned in an effort to remove Amber Heard from the production of Aquaman 2, now titled Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom. Of course, it appears their efforts have so far failed – especially Amber Heard has already been training to appear in the new film. With this, Depp has something to say. Be sure to watch the whole video and in addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
